## Title: DDPositions
## APIVersion: 101048, 101049
## Version: 3.3.0
## Author: |cFF9B15@Konten|r
## SavedVariables: DDPositions_SavedVars
## Description: Displays DPS role assignments and positions for trial zones. Includes manual and free assignment modes, UI toggling, and zone-based role logic.

## Change Log:
## Version 3.3.0:
## - Removed unfinished group join/leave notification functions (will be reintroduced in a future update).
## - Improved overall stability.
## - Fixed minor issues.

## Version 3.2.0:
## - Restored the /DDPositions command to open/close the panel without requiring a keybind.
## - Fixed minor bugs.
## - Added open license.

## Version 3.1.3:
## - Fixed minor bugs.
## - Added assignments for the following trials:
##   Hel Ra Citadel
##   Aetherian Archive
##   Halls of Fabrication
##   Ossein Cage

## Version 3.1.2:
## - Fixed minor bugs.
## 
## Version 3.1.1:
## - Fixed minor bugs.

## Version 3.1.0:
## - Fixed minor bugs.
## - Added Manual assignments.
## - Added Free assignments.

## Version 3.0.0:
## - Complete rework of addon functionality.
## - Interface updates and improvements.
## - Improved zone detection and role handling.
## - Fixed rare UI overlap when toggling the panel.
## - Various quality-of-life fixes.
## - Enhanced overall UI/UX.

## Version 2.0.0:
## - Added Panel UI with keybind visibility toggle.
## - Improved readability of position markers.
## - Fixed saved variable load order.

## Version 1.0.0:
## - Displays DPS role positions for trial zones.
## - Initial release!

